1
00:00:01,860 --> 00:00:05,030
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Come on, get moving!</b></font>

2
00:00:06,280 --> 00:00:08,240
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Are you refusing a direct order?</b></font>

3
00:00:08,240 --> 00:00:09,980
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>B-But...</b></font>

4
00:00:09,980 --> 00:00:13,590
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Just shut up and do as I say! Go!</b></font>

5
00:00:18,510 --> 00:00:21,070
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Ugh, how useless.</b></font>

6
00:00:21,070 --> 00:00:25,930
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Garbage doesn't need to think.
It only needs to do as I say.</b></font>

7
00:00:27,070 --> 00:00:29,590
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'm going to become king.</b></font>

8
00:00:30,030 --> 00:00:31,660
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Stop this, Nai!</b></font>

9
00:00:32,180 --> 00:00:36,580
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>No matter how comfortable, 
chains are still chains.</b></font>

10
00:00:36,580 --> 00:00:42,550
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>But we're different. You and I have
 our own will, and we walk freely.</b></font>

11
00:00:42,550 --> 00:00:44,440
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b><i>This</i> is power!</b></font>

12
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:56,540
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Just wait for a short while. 
A mere century or so.</b></font>

13
00:00:56,940 --> 00:01:00,120
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I promise I'll build a world of plants.</b></font>

14
00:02:56,780 --> 00:02:59,530
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>It was him! I'm sure of it!</b></font>

15
00:02:59,530 --> 00:03:03,520
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>So come on, give me the bounty! 
All $$6 billion!</b></font>

16
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:07,010
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Why would anyone pay you? 
It's not like you caught the guy.</b></font>

17
00:03:07,010 --> 00:03:09,830
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Okay, just half is fine! 
Or even a third!</b></font>

18
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:11,960
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I called it in, right?</b></font>

19
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:14,750
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Don't waste your breath on us. 
Go talk to HQ.</b></font>

20
00:03:14,750 --> 00:03:20,570
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Not that anybody cares 
about bounties anymore anyway.</b></font>

21
00:03:20,570 --> 00:03:22,830
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>{\an8}Come on, that's cruel!</b></font>

22
00:03:20,570 --> 00:03:25,230
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Hey, reporter lady. Is this another 
one of those "lost technology" things?</b></font>

23
00:03:25,230 --> 00:03:28,470
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>My coworker said she's sure it is.</b></font>

24
00:03:28,470 --> 00:03:32,930
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>In six months or so, this... 
No, something even more impressive</b></font>

25
00:03:32,930 --> 00:03:35,770
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>is going to arrive in droves 
on our planet, right?</b></font>

26
00:03:35,770 --> 00:03:38,110
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'll probably lose my job
at that point, but...</b></font>

27
00:03:38,650 --> 00:03:40,670
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I still can't wait.</b></font>

28
00:03:40,670 --> 00:03:42,750
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Indeed, I can't wait!</b></font>

29
00:03:51,810 --> 00:03:52,920
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Meryl!</b></font>

30
00:03:53,620 --> 00:03:55,810
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>It sounds like it's gotta be Vash!</b></font>

31
00:03:55,810 --> 00:03:58,520
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>They say he left town with a girl!</b></font>

32
00:04:00,190 --> 00:04:02,410
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Still no response?</b></font>

33
00:04:02,410 --> 00:04:03,500
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>No.</b></font>

34
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:07,820
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Okay, so something happened 
in this "Home" place,</b></font>

35
00:04:07,820 --> 00:04:11,850
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>and this girl came flying over 
to warn Vash about it...</b></font>

36
00:04:11,850 --> 00:04:13,850
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>And then they both left for "Home."</b></font>

37
00:04:13,850 --> 00:04:15,860
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Sounds reasonable, right?</b></font>

38
00:04:16,250 --> 00:04:17,960
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Then we should also—</b></font>

39
00:04:17,960 --> 00:04:22,700
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>But of course! Journalists 
must be quick and brave.</b></font>

40
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:27,590
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'm starting to run low.</b></font>

41
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:33,770
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Hey, what?! Wait, ladies!</b></font>

42
00:04:33,770 --> 00:04:35,710
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>You forgot to load me!</b></font>

43
00:04:36,420 --> 00:04:39,190
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I said wait, damn it!</b></font>

44
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:51,520
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>The shields are down.</b></font>

45
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:54,080
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I hope everyone's okay.</b></font>

46
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:55,740
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>They're okay, right?</b></font>

47
00:05:00,810 --> 00:05:02,040
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Vash?</b></font>

48
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:05,830
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Let's go.</b></font>

49
00:05:22,970 --> 00:05:26,180
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Hey, is anyone here?</b></font>

50
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:29,140
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Could it be...</b></font>

51
00:05:29,140 --> 00:05:31,920
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Brad said he'd hold out, right?</b></font>

52
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:34,460
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>He's a man of his word.</b></font>

53
00:05:34,460 --> 00:05:36,320
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>They must all be sheltering somewhere—</b></font>

54
00:05:39,140 --> 00:05:40,300
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Vash?</b></font>

55
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:53,660
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>If he's here...</b></font>

56
00:06:06,890 --> 00:06:07,940
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Nai?</b></font>

57
00:06:12,580 --> 00:06:13,890
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Who's there?!</b></font>

58
00:06:29,330 --> 00:06:30,340
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Vash?</b></font>

59
00:06:32,250 --> 00:06:33,210
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Let's go.</b></font>

60
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:52,180
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Jessica, stay close.</b></font>

61
00:06:53,970 --> 00:06:54,730
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Jessica?</b></font>

62
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:57,560
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Jessica?! Where are you?!</b></font>

63
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,650
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Answer me!</b></font>

64
00:06:58,650 --> 00:06:59,970
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Vash.</b></font>

65
00:07:03,950 --> 00:07:05,080
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Nai!</b></font>

66
00:07:05,650 --> 00:07:07,700
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>First, let me thank you.</b></font>

67
00:07:08,020 --> 00:07:12,100
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>With your help, I was able to take out 
the trash from JuLai...</b></font>

68
00:07:12,530 --> 00:07:14,000
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Hundreds of thousands of them.</b></font>

69
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,570
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Nai...</b></font>

70
00:07:15,570 --> 00:07:17,210
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Rejoice, brother.</b></font>

71
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:22,200
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>We meet again. Thank you for coming.</b></font>

72
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:24,410
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>So you lured me back to Home?</b></font>

73
00:07:24,820 --> 00:07:27,240
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Where is everyone else?!</b></font>

74
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:30,280
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>They're safe. For now.</b></font>

75
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:32,640
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>However...</b></font>

76
00:07:34,180 --> 00:07:35,230
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Jessica!</b></font>

77
00:07:35,230 --> 00:07:36,340
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Vash!</b></font>

78
00:07:36,340 --> 00:07:41,400
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Whether they stay that way
 is up to you, Vash.</b></font>

79
00:07:44,390 --> 00:07:49,140
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Vash, come with me. 
Swear your cooperation to me.</b></font>

80
00:07:52,330 --> 00:07:54,810
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>You never change.</b></font>

81
00:07:55,610 --> 00:07:58,920
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I just have to motivate you, then.</b></font>

82
00:07:59,470 --> 00:08:03,380
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'm going to kill the trash here 
on Ship Three, one by one.</b></font>

83
00:08:03,690 --> 00:08:06,240
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Until you change your mind.</b></font>

84
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,260
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>All while you watch.</b></font>

85
00:08:07,580 --> 00:08:08,340
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Nai!</b></font>

86
00:08:08,340 --> 00:08:12,730
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Nai is dead! I am Millions Knives!</b></font>

87
00:08:12,730 --> 00:08:15,270
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>This brat goes first!</b></font>

88
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:16,430
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Stop!</b></font>

89
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,570
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Jessica!</b></font>

90
00:08:26,300 --> 00:08:27,510
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Are you—</b></font>

91
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:45,020
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>As long as you refuse to pledge
 cooperation with Lord Knives,</b></font>

92
00:08:45,020 --> 00:08:49,180
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>you will continue to bear witness 
to the death of trash.</b></font>

93
00:08:50,030 --> 00:08:53,550
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>How much of it can you take?</b></font>

94
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:58,640
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Ten of them? Twenty, perhaps?</b></font>

95
00:09:01,630 --> 00:09:03,870
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Now...</b></font>

96
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:06,610
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>What say you?</b></font>

97
00:09:04,900 --> 00:09:07,480
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>{\an8}Jessica, hold your breath!</b></font>

98
00:09:10,950 --> 00:09:13,070
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Fire extinguisher activating.</b></font>

99
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:29,370
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'm glad that worked.</b></font>

100
00:09:29,370 --> 00:09:30,550
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

101
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:34,820
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Hey, Vash! That puppet said that
everyone's safe, right?!</b></font>

102
00:09:34,820 --> 00:09:40,310
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Yeah. Which means we've got to do 
something about the puppeteer.</b></font>

103
00:09:40,310 --> 00:09:42,460
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>But where could he be?</b></font>

104
00:09:42,460 --> 00:09:43,380
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I know.</b></font>

105
00:09:43,380 --> 00:09:44,020
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Huh?</b></font>

106
00:09:44,020 --> 00:09:47,700
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>The puppeteer is controlling his puppets
from somewhere else.</b></font>

107
00:09:47,700 --> 00:09:49,070
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Which could only be through...</b></font>

108
00:09:49,580 --> 00:09:52,280
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Oh! The surveillance cameras!</b></font>

109
00:09:53,030 --> 00:09:56,030
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Yes, the security room.</b></font>

110
00:10:12,670 --> 00:10:15,230
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Vash the Stampede!</b></font>

111
00:10:15,230 --> 00:10:17,520
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I see. I see now.</b></font>

112
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:20,760
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>You're no ordinary trash!</b></font>

113
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:25,290
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>You are Lord Knives's brother, after all!</b></font>

114
00:10:26,050 --> 00:10:30,530
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Nevertheless, you are wandering 
into your own demise.</b></font>

115
00:10:30,530 --> 00:10:32,440
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Capture him!</b></font>

116
00:10:56,140 --> 00:10:59,330
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Hesitation can prove fatal!</b></font>

117
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:08,240
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>My treasure, given to me by Lord Knives...</b></font>

118
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:13,080
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>This royal treasure
 has made me a king.</b></font>

119
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:17,340
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>It cannot be destroyed so easily!</b></font>

120
00:11:42,290 --> 00:11:43,410
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Vash!</b></font>

121
00:11:46,910 --> 00:11:48,060
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Is that...</b></font>

122
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,960
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>The research dome.</b></font>

123
00:11:51,370 --> 00:11:53,530
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Jessica, I need your help.</b></font>

124
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:55,450
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Listen carefully.</b></font>

125
00:12:22,370 --> 00:12:27,690
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Oh, did you lock me in?</b></font>

126
00:12:28,250 --> 00:12:32,020
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Am I a cornered rat? No, no.</b></font>

127
00:12:32,020 --> 00:12:34,730
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>You are the rat.</b></font>

128
00:12:35,530 --> 00:12:40,460
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I, Leonof the Puppetmaster, 
king of puppets,</b></font>

129
00:12:40,460 --> 00:12:45,430
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>shall capture you and 
take you to Lord Knives.</b></font>

130
00:12:45,430 --> 00:12:46,670
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I won't let you.</b></font>

131
00:12:46,670 --> 00:12:48,580
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>But I will regardless.</b></font>

132
00:12:49,010 --> 00:12:53,990
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Let's begin the puppet show!</b></font>

133
00:13:33,430 --> 00:13:36,360
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Show yourself, Puppetmaster!</b></font>

134
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:41,650
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I refuse! What do you think 
these puppets are for?!</b></font>

135
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:44,930
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Jessica!</b></font>

136
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:48,450
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>There!</b></font>

137
00:14:05,640 --> 00:14:08,090
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'm telling you, this is futile!</b></font>

138
00:14:10,980 --> 00:14:14,810
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Did you think I'd lose control 
of my puppets in zero gravity?</b></font>

139
00:14:14,810 --> 00:14:17,710
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Wrong! So wrong!</b></font>

140
00:14:17,710 --> 00:14:21,400
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Lord Knives would be disappointed!</b></font>

141
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:28,910
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Capture complete. How easy that was.</b></font>

142
00:14:28,910 --> 00:14:33,180
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Were the others who lost 
to you even trying?</b></font>

143
00:14:33,830 --> 00:14:36,780
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Lord Knives, wait for me!</b></font>

144
00:14:36,780 --> 00:14:39,770
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I will bring him to you soon!</b></font>

145
00:14:40,100 --> 00:14:43,090
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>You won't be taking me anywhere.</b></font>

146
00:14:43,090 --> 00:14:44,530
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Oh?</b></font>

147
00:14:44,530 --> 00:14:48,910
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Are you saying you have another 
trick up your sleeve? In this state?</b></font>

148
00:14:48,910 --> 00:14:51,090
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>That's right. Jessica!</b></font>

149
00:15:09,610 --> 00:15:15,230
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>My puppets, your king orders you...</b></font>

150
00:15:26,980 --> 00:15:28,110
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Vash...</b></font>

151
00:15:52,810 --> 00:15:56,640
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>This puppet show is over!</b></font>

152
00:16:08,910 --> 00:16:10,160
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Vash!</b></font>

153
00:16:25,290 --> 00:16:26,530
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Nobody...</b></font>

154
00:16:27,160 --> 00:16:30,300
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Nobody ever paid attention to me.</b></font>

155
00:16:31,010 --> 00:16:37,270
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>The only ones who saw me were 
Lord Knives and the Eye of Michael.</b></font>

156
00:16:37,900 --> 00:16:42,190
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>This isn't over yet, Vash the Stampede.</b></font>

157
00:16:42,190 --> 00:16:45,530
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'm taking you with me!</b></font>

158
00:16:54,160 --> 00:16:56,980
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>You're as soft as ever.</b></font>

159
00:16:58,460 --> 00:17:01,500
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Keep your guard up till the end.</b></font>

160
00:17:12,190 --> 00:17:13,920
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>What are you doing?</b></font>

161
00:17:14,320 --> 00:17:17,690
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Oh, just checking to see 
if you're a puppet.</b></font>

162
00:17:18,550 --> 00:17:19,980
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>What does that even mean?</b></font>

163
00:17:20,420 --> 00:17:24,940
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Yeah... It's really you, 
isn't it, Wolfwood?</b></font>

164
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:27,570
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>This isn't over!</b></font>

165
00:17:30,770 --> 00:17:33,860
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Lord Knives made me a king.</b></font>

166
00:17:34,220 --> 00:17:37,210
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>To serve him, I...</b></font>

167
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:49,170
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Sorry about this,</b></font>

168
00:17:49,170 --> 00:17:50,800
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Leonof.</b></font>

169
00:17:50,800 --> 00:17:52,180
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Wolfwood!</b></font>

170
00:18:17,080 --> 00:18:20,760
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Meryl Stryfe here from 
the Bernardelli News Agency.</b></font>

171
00:18:20,760 --> 00:18:23,160
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Likewise, Milly Thompson!</b></font>

172
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:25,230
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Oh, it's nice to meet you.</b></font>

173
00:18:25,230 --> 00:18:28,450
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>And, uh, long time no see, M-Meryl...</b></font>

174
00:18:28,450 --> 00:18:29,740
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>It's Meryl Stryfe!</b></font>

175
00:18:29,740 --> 00:18:30,990
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>And I'm Milly Thompson!</b></font>

176
00:18:30,990 --> 00:18:32,510
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'm glad to see you're well.</b></font>

177
00:18:32,510 --> 00:18:33,430
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'm Meryl!</b></font>

178
00:18:33,430 --> 00:18:34,220
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>And I'm Milly!</b></font>

179
00:18:44,530 --> 00:18:48,710
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>You said nobody ever paid 
attention to you, right?</b></font>

180
00:18:48,710 --> 00:18:50,450
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>That's not true.</b></font>

181
00:18:52,300 --> 00:18:55,230
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>When you recover, let's sit down and talk,</b></font>

182
00:18:55,820 --> 00:18:59,160
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Leonof the Puppetmaster, or rather...</b></font>

183
00:18:59,560 --> 00:19:00,820
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Emilio.</b></font>

184
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:07,170
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

185
00:19:24,520 --> 00:19:27,030
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Where in the world were you?</b></font>

186
00:19:27,030 --> 00:19:31,350
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Sorry. With those puppets everywhere, 
we couldn't get out of the shelter.</b></font>

187
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:33,250
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'm glad you're all safe.</b></font>

188
00:19:33,250 --> 00:19:38,740
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Yeah. We owe it all to Jessica 
for going to fetch him.</b></font>

189
00:19:38,740 --> 00:19:41,230
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Does it hurt? Are you all right?</b></font>

190
00:19:41,230 --> 00:19:44,950
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Don't worry. Thanks for your help earlier.</b></font>

191
00:19:45,490 --> 00:19:49,660
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>It's thanks to you that I was able 
to protect the folks here at Home.</b></font>

192
00:19:50,040 --> 00:19:51,250
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

193
00:19:51,250 --> 00:19:52,680
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Vash.</b></font>

194
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:54,090
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Luida...</b></font>

195
00:19:59,820 --> 00:20:02,830
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I've done something unforgivable.</b></font>

196
00:20:04,290 --> 00:20:06,770
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I wasn't able to stop Nai.</b></font>

197
00:20:07,330 --> 00:20:10,020
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>On top of that, I... JuLai...</b></font>

198
00:20:11,650 --> 00:20:14,510
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I visited many times 
over the last 150 years.</b></font>

199
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:17,040
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>There were so many people there.</b></font>

200
00:20:17,040 --> 00:20:24,130
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>They smiled at me, gave me water, 
shared bread with me.</b></font>

201
00:20:25,170 --> 00:20:31,840
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Mary, Ken, Takeshi, Ange, Jiro...</b></font>

202
00:20:32,450 --> 00:20:34,880
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>And also Roberto.</b></font>

203
00:20:35,660 --> 00:20:37,090
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Vash...</b></font>

204
00:20:37,670 --> 00:20:41,640
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Maybe I should have died, too. But...</b></font>

205
00:20:41,970 --> 00:20:45,430
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>You... live to suffer.</b></font>

206
00:20:45,990 --> 00:20:47,440
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I...</b></font>

207
00:20:47,440 --> 00:20:49,190
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>There's no need to apologize.</b></font>

208
00:20:49,710 --> 00:20:52,910
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>You tried to walk the right path.</b></font>

209
00:20:53,510 --> 00:20:59,460
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>The result was unfortunate, but the 
responsibility lies with every one of us</b></font>

210
00:20:59,460 --> 00:21:01,160
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>living on this planet.</b></font>

211
00:21:02,060 --> 00:21:06,870
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Tell me more of the people 
who passed away in JuLai.</b></font>

212
00:21:06,870 --> 00:21:08,280
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Luida...</b></font>

213
00:21:08,280 --> 00:21:10,190
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Tell me, too!</b></font>

214
00:21:10,620 --> 00:21:15,320
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>The weight you bear, 
this tremendously heavy burden...</b></font>

215
00:21:15,320 --> 00:21:19,870
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>We want to help you carry it, 
even if only a little.</b></font>

216
00:21:19,870 --> 00:21:22,640
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>You're not in this fight alone.</b></font>

217
00:21:23,080 --> 00:21:25,600
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>So... So...</b></font>

218
00:21:28,180 --> 00:21:30,270
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>That's right, Vash!</b></font>

219
00:21:30,270 --> 00:21:31,950
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Sure is.</b></font>

220
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,400
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Yeah!</b></font>

221
00:21:40,570 --> 00:21:42,800
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Welcome back, Vash.</b></font>

222
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:48,270
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>I'm home.</b></font>

223
00:21:55,800 --> 00:21:59,310
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>What's this? From the Puppetmaster?</b></font>

224
00:22:01,600 --> 00:22:05,640
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Great news! We found your brother.</b></font>

225
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:10,470
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>The time to awake is nigh.</b></font>

226
00:22:10,470 --> 00:22:13,300
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>Right, Lord Knives?</b></font>

227
00:23:50,280 --> 00:23:54,330
<font face="Gandhi Sans" size="24"><b>We're all birds of a feather, after all.</b></font>

